  "dialogue": {
    "5": {
      "id": "5",
      "speaker": "Narrator",
      "text": "*These notes are no mere diary. These are the visions of Karsus himself. Designs for the crown he hoped to forge, and the new form of magic he planned to create with it.*",
      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale ponders after having read a book with potentially world-changing knowledge within. The book is open in his hands, but not in shot.",
      "checkflags": [],
      "setflags": [
        "ORI_Gale_Knows_ReadKarsusNotes"
      ],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "18",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "4": {
          "id": "4",
          "speaker": "Narrator",
          "text": "*He almost succeeded. The crown sits atop the elder brain, and the Karsite Weave rests within your chest, incomplete but already capable of immense destruction.*",
          "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale ponders after having read a book with potentially world-changing knowledge within (book does not need to be shown)",
          "checkflags": [
            "ORI_Gale_Knows_KarsiteWeave"
          ],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "18",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "15": {
              "id": "15",
              "speaker": "Narrator",
              "text": "*Reunite the crown with the Dead Three's Netherstones, and you would have total control over it. The power of a god, in your hands.*",
              "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale ponders after having read a book with potentially world-changing knowledge within (book does not need to be shown)",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "18",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "10": {
                  "id": "10",
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "The broken artefacts of a failed god. The crown should be destroyed, before it causes any more damage.",
                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale ponders after having read a book with potentially world-changing knowledge within (book does not need to be shown)",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "18",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "9": {
                      "id": "9",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Though Karsus could only have worn the crown for mere moments, he managed to destroy an empire, killing thousands in the process.",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "18",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "6": {
                          "id": "6",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*In the hands of the Dead Three's Chosen, it threatens to do much the same. You must find a way to stop them, to render the crown harmless. Detonating the power of the Karsite Weave, if necessary.*",
                          "context": "",
                          "checkflags": [
                            "ORI_Gale_Knows_KarsiteWeave"
                          ],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "18",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "18": {
                              "id": "18",
                              "speaker": "Narrator",
                              "text": "*You can save Faer\u00fbn from Karsus' evil, and the Absolute's in one fell swoop. Only, you might not live to enjoy it.*",
                              "context": "",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "",
                              "is_end": true,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {}
                            }
                          }
                        },
                        "13": {
                          "id": "13",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*In the hands of the Dead Three's Chosen, it threatens to do much the same. You must find a way to stop them, to render the crown harmless. Detonating the orb, if necessary.*",
