                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "3": {
                      "id": "3",
                      "speaker": "Narrator",
                      "text": "*Between you and the crown there's the small matter of the elder brain to contend with. Not to mention the deal you made with Raphael.*",
                      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Gale ponders after having read a book with potentially world-changing knowledge within (book does not need to be shown)",
