                        "2": {
                          "id": "2",
                          "speaker": "Narrator",
                          "text": "*For now, whatever designs of your own with regards to the crown will have to wait. But not for long. It will be in your hands soon enough, and you have quite the decision to make.*",
                          "context": "",
